{"tid":1115690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"指抖音國際版對兒童有害　印度法院命下架","createTime":"2019-04-19T11:11:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T16:03:03.000Z","uid":47714,"like":63,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"18e2d6b0ae6bf0d41ba7689b4469a869e914e501","tid":1115690,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T11:11:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/posts/10157590013777448\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fposts%2F10157590013777448&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSSLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=7e793da1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/posts/10157590013777448</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gLXbuZS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgLXbuZS.png&h=f87ec365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國開發短片分享軟件抖音熱爆全球，惟印度一家法院近日判定抖音國際版「對兒童有害」，要求禁止該軟件在印度下載，印度Google Play store在周二已經應要求將手機軟件下架。"},{"pid":"056ebe3aa9c85391f72a92b247dbf1ac711666a3","tid":1115690,"uid":6058,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T11:17:58.000Z","msg":"呢個apps有害係真係好多報告都有講<br />\n真係會睇壞腦"},{"pid":"c01d38e6cc1708085ad4574eea98b15d332591f2","tid":1115690,"uid":41500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T11:20:40.000Z","msg":"所有禁毒標語 將毒品取代成抖音 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都係果句<br />\n乜野抖音呀呢到冇人識你呀 走音我就識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e0457f0504010f470ee6a0f9a43d7de639c7c3f","tid":1115690,"uid":35430,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T11:23:58.000Z","msg":"支那壞腦文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全球淪陷<br />\n我就逢共就必反，冇裝過抖音<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e16ebffe7678eb72bfcb1ce6a37ba6717bec435","tid":1115690,"uid":90820,"l